Look who we spotted at the table next to ours at lunch… little Canyon sporting a bib from the Bison set. Isn’t he adorable? His mom says she loves putting him in this bib with his mini jean-jacket. 😊 

After saying hi to Canyon we offered them a store credit and took a photo together. So today is the start of something new! Whenever one of us sees your little ones out & about wearing Copper Pearl we will say hello & give you a store credit! 

There’s nothing more fun for us than spotting CP in the wild! 🥰 #CPinthewild

What’s your baby wearing out and about today? 👇🏾

📣 Calling all mamas! We’ve got a new mom hack for you🚨

We’re a team full of moms over here at Copper Pearl HQ and we want to share some of our favorite mom hacks!

This $10 laundry tote is the most versatile bag you’ll ever own! It’s collapsible, light weight, and cute! We use it as a catch all bag for the car, grocery bag tote, and a pool bag! We’re sure there a dozen other ways this thing could come in handy, don’t you think?! 🙌🏼
